summary: I love language. It's the reason I  enjoyed working in libraries in the Netherlands and Ireland for so long. During that time I have done many diffrent tasks where this quality came in very useful. I have done translation work and noticed it's not only something I'm good at but also enjoy very much. My love for the Dutch and English language combined with my eye for detail and accuracy. It's the reason why I have decided to start working as a freelance translator English/Dutch and Dutch/English.
